Package: plmr
Title: Probabilistic Learning on Manifolds in R
Description: R Implementation of methods for probabilistic learning on manifolds (PLoM),
	     e.g. diffusion maps reduce basis MCMC sampling, ridge estimation,
	     normal-bundle bootstrap, diffusion sampling, manifold scaffold,
	     manifold-constrained inference, optimization, etc.
Authors@R: person('Ruda', 'Zhang', , 'rudazhan@gmail.com', c('cre', 'aut'))
